# nesref ships only its own source (frontend.cpp, libretro.h, build.bat, README).
# Everything below is supplied locally by the developer and is deliberately NOT
# committed — chiefly to keep separately-licensed binaries out of this repo
# (libretro cores carry their own, sometimes non-commercial, licenses; SDL2
# binaries ship under zlib).

# SDL2 runtime DLL (copied next to the exe from runner/external/SDL2 by build.bat)
SDL2*.dll
SDL2-*/

# libretro NES core binaries — supply at runtime as argv[1].
# (e.g. nestopia_libretro.dll, fceumm_libretro.dll)
cores/
*_libretro.dll
*_libretro.dll.zip

# build + run artifacts
nesref.exe
*.obj
*.exe
nes_state*.bin
nes_trace.jsonl
*.wav
*_out.txt
*_err.txt
